# Dizcus

Built using Vue.js (TypeScript) for the frontend and FastAPI + SQLModel + MySQL for the backend.

## 🚀 Features

- 🔑 User Authentication — OAuth2 + JWT for secure login & signup
- 💬 Messaging System — send, receive, and persist messages across sessions
- 🗂️ Database Integration — MySQL with SQLModel for users, chats, and message history
- 🎨 Frontend — Vue.js + TypeScript, component-based UI (TopBar, SideBar, MessageBox)
- 📡 API Communication — Axios with Bearer tokens for authenticated requests
- ⚡ Designed for quick team communication in workplace settings 


